# Orchestrator context

## Core subsystems (shipped — do not re-implement)

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Audit canonical + ingest | `core/audit/` |
| Event bus + outbox | `core/bus/` |
| MCP driver host | `core/drivers/`, `vault/.system/drivers.json.example` |
| Governed runs | `core/execution/service.py`, `core/graphs/pipeline_graph.py` |
| Approval interrupts | `core/kernel/interrupts.py` |
| Tier B hook bootstrap | `core/audit/hook_bootstrap.py` |

**Ground rules:** one process; MCP replaces tools not graphs; keep `registry.py` (pipeline only); no Docker default.

